Asma Fayyaz, 23, was horrifically scarred three years ago after falling into a pan of boiling fat when she slipped in her kitchen.

She had a new right eyebrow and a right eyelash transplanted by Dr Shahmalak and his team from Crown Clinic, based in Manchester. 

Mona Bhatti, 42, has also been given new eyebrows. She was shunned by Pakistani society after having a sex change operation. Born a man, she was splattered with acid while begging on the streets after changing sex to a woman. 

